- State management:
  - Use React with useState/useEffect; no global state library required for MVP.
  - Initialize arrays with useState<Type[]>([]) and ensure type safety.
  - Guard all API data with: const narratives = Array.isArray(data?.narratives) ? data.narratives : [].
